title: HD 1080P Car Dual Lens Dash Cam Front/Rear/Inside Video Recorder Camera G-sensor
item_description:
HD 1080P Car Dual Lens Dash Cam Front/Rear/Inside Video Recorder Camera G-sensor
HD 1080P Dual Dash Camera
 Product Feature
3 Camera 1080P FHD Dash Cam:
With 2.0 inch LCD screen,the dashcam front and rear simultaneously capture the road front, rear and inside passenger cabin at dual 1920x1080P, capturing every detail of the vehicle while driving. Best choice for online car-hailing service, taxis/rideshare drivers, commuters, and families.
Night Vision & WDR/HDR Tech:
The dashcam interior facing camera with 4 infrared LED lights, combined with super big aperture, wide dynamic range(WDR) and high dynamic range(HDR), you can get clearer footage and image at night. Car plates license can be easily seen even in darkness.
Seamless Loop Recording:
The dash cam with loop recording overwrites the unlocked oldest file automatically when the TF card is full, to ensure the normal recording.
Built-in G-sensor:
G-sensor is activated by any collision to start recording emergency video to help you get evidence in the car recorder when the unexpected situation occurs.
24 Hours Parking Monitoring:
While your car is parked and the engine is off the dual dash cam front and inside auto-start and record a short video once it detects bumps by someone in parking, then turns off automatically. These dashcams for cars' videos will be saved & locked, thus providing you with video evidence. The dashcam front and cabin need a constant power supply either from the external battery pack or hardwire.
Easy Installation & Use:
This dash camera is very easy to install and operate. Just insert the TF card (not included) and connect to the power supply. The car dash camera will start recording immediately after igniting, shut down and save the video when you shut off the engine.
Product Specification
Type: 3Camera 1080P Car Dash Camera
Pixel: 1920x1080/30 frames
Display Screen: 2.0 inch IPS HD 4:3
Viewing Angle: 170(Front)/110(Rear)/120(Inside) degrees
Front Camera: 6-Glass/F2.0 aperture
Special Functions: Cycle recording/G-sensor/24h Parking Monitor/Motion Detection/Night Vision/WDR/HDR
Memory Card: Maximum 32G
Power Interface: USB2.0/5V 1.5A
Battery: 320mAh polymer lithium battery
Current Frequency: 50/60HZ
Language: English, Chinese, Korean, Russian, Japanese, French, Italian, German, etc.
Operation/Storage Temp: -40+70 degrees
Package Included
🎁 1 x 1080P Dual Dash Cam
🎁 1 x Car charger
🎁 1 x Suction cup holder
🎁 1 x Rear Camera
🎁 1 x Video Cable
🎁 1 x User Manual
